data.description: Remarks: Stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in Redstone commons complete with a covered back porch, 2 car garage, and fenced in backyard. The open kitchen features a spacious island, stainless appliances, and granite countertops. The kitchen opens to the great room with easy access to the covered porch. The primary suite is just off the back side of the house & primary bath features a walk-in closet, dual sinks, and a large shower.
